# INTRODUCTION

> “Productivity is not about doing more.  
> It is about eliminating the unnecessary.”

Welcome to **Prompt Mastery 2025**, a modern guide designed to help you achieve more in less time using AI-powered workflows.

This book focuses on **practical execution**, not theory.

If used daily, the workflows in this book can save you **1–3 hours every single day**.

