# PART II — WORK WORKFLOWS  

---

# EMAIL OVERHAUL WORKFLOW

### GOAL  
Reduce email processing time by 70%.

### PROMPT  
```
Act as my executive email assistant.
Summarize all emails.
Classify as: Urgent / Important / Low Priority.
Draft responses in my tone (professional + calm).
Create a follow-up list with deadlines.
```

---

<div style="page-break-after: always;"></div>

---

# MEETING SUMMARIES & ACTION PLANS  

### PROMPT  
```
Act as my meeting analyst.
Turn this transcript into:
• Summary
• Action items
• Decisions
• Deadlines
• Risks
```

